data.description: Welcome home to this well-maintained bi-level home on a 1/4+ acre corner lot near shopping, Ft. Carson, & Peterson AFB! 2018 Class IV roof and in 2019, the kitchen was remodeled to include all the stainless appliances (the inspired chef will love the gas cooktop & dual convection ovens), additional cabinetry added, all cabinets stained, granite countertops, & the space was transformed into open-concept w/a large island. And you'll surely appreciate the reverse osmosis water systems found in the kitchen sink & refrigerator, not to mention found in the lower-level kitchenette full-size refrigerator as well. You'll also appreciate the large entryway/mudroom and the skylights allowing for additional light to enter the home. On both levels, take notice of the newly added Pergo pet safe LVP flooring. In 2021, a high-efficiency furnace to keep those heating costs down was added along w/a whole house purifier to keep allergies at bay. Also in 2021, an on-demand hot water heater was installed & in 2023, a steam humidifier was added. In the primary ensuite, you'll find dual sinks & in the finished lower level, you'll find a wet bar, fireplace, 3/4 bath, large bedroom, spacious laundry room w/extra cabinetry and laundry sink, crawl space with ample height for additional storage, and an expansive room now being utilized as an exercise room (pre-wired for sound) but could also be utilized for an office or to fit whatever multitude of needs your family has. The exterior was painted in 2018. The large yard with automated sprinkler system is like a haven with multiple fruit trees, garden boxes, firepit, RV parking, and a shed with a new roof & new siding. The backyard is completely fenced so the children and fur-babies can roam free! And be sure to take note that this beautiful home has a south-facing driveway to keep the snow at bay and a north-facing backyard to allow for cool lounging in the hot summer months. Come and see this beauty today!
